<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>As agreed when you purchased your policy, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">we attempted to take payment on [insert date here]</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">. Unfortunately, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">this payment was unsuccessful</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>We will automatically re-attempt this payment within the next few days</b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">, please ensure that you have funds available.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please note that </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">if we are unable to take payment for your policy then this may result in your policy being cancelled</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>If you wish to discuss this, please feel free to contact us on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
